            <varlistentry>
                <term><emphasis>Returns</emphasis>&nbsp;:</term>
                <listitem><simpara>a list of gtk.Action objects</simpara></listitem>
            </varlistentry>
          </variablelist>

          <para>
            The <methodname>get_file_actions</methodname>() method returns a list of
            gtk.Action objects.
